{"tid":1457974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失你老母敗咩死黑警 成功癱瘓十四個鐘呀","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:19.000Z","uid":64275,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8aaa1e5a11e8ed2016f38e84b44cb7d82f222be0","tid":1457974,"uid":64275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:41:04.000Z","msg":"【果燃台Live】機場停運14小時！機管局視運作情況 明早6時重新編配航班<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190812&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59922119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190812%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59922119&d=5%2F0N1eX%2FnGDFGLWAFE16zkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=cb615690\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190812%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59922119&h=f624032b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190812&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59922119</a><br />\n<br />\n成班黑警淨係迫散播失敗論？Sorry我地唔會比你分化到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日再黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要同散水撚割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5d5de9d7bd480f33cf361a0e03384370522b3a71","tid":1457974,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"d5abd779558de18d5353d8177e621c3e6e194ac4","tid":1457974,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:41:48.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用下個腦諗嘢<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n你哋唔好喺度發文喺度煽動<br />\n佢地成功分化我地了啦<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里而的大反派說了這麼幾句 <br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後這再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"14e7b4d8b4329c5d3a1161adca8b51a4857f0598","tid":1457974,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"咪係 <br />\n怪人地散水既人 真係唔知咩居心"},{"pid":"7491c2f7d4a1cf38f4f5edfd59377096b3a3eb93","tid":1457974,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"所謂輿論就係將贏既野講做輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d6611950ddbdeb4507cde7f3a80b2140752b5c8","tid":1457974,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"721 811"}]}